title: MAKE AN IMPACT
itunes:title: MAKE AN IMPACT
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
MAKE AN IMPACT! Are you ready for your life to begin? Now is your time to build your legacy mindset and make an impact on the world! Listen to this every morning and your life will begin to change. One of the Best Motivational Speeches Ever featuring Pastor and Motivational Speaker Brian Bullock (https://bit.ly/BrianBullockMotiversity).


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).
